37 SECTION 2.(b) In the event that the total amount of grant awards for the 2025-2026
38 or 2026-2027 fiscal year to participating community colleges in areas listed in subsection (a) of
39 this section is less than two million dollars ($2,000,000), the State Board may use those funds to
40 award grants to participating community colleges that are not located in those areas.
41 SECTION 3. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Community
42 Colleges System Office the sum of five million dollars ($5,000,000) in recurring funds for the
43 2025-2026 fiscal year to implement the provisions of this act.
44 SECTION 4. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
